\id 2TI  
\h Timɔte II 
\mt1 TIRERU YIRUSE TE PƆLU 
\mt1 U TIMƆTE KUA 
\ip Sɑnɑm mɛ Pɔlu u Timɔte tireru yiruse te yoruɑ u wɑ̃ɑwɑ pirisɔm sɔɔ Romuɔ, u kɑ ɡɔɔ mɑrɑ, wiru 4:6-8. U Timɔte kɑnɑ u nùn nɑɑmwɛmɑ kpɑ u kɑ nùn win purɑn yɑberu nɑɑwɑ kɑ sere mɑɑ win tirenu ɡɑnu mì sɔɔ Gusunɔn ɡɑri yoruɑ. U mɑɑ Timɔte yiiremɔ u de u n sɑ̃ɑ nɑɑnɛɡii Yesun mi kɑ sere Lɑbɑɑri ɡeɑn kpɑrɑbu sɔɔ. U mɑɑ nùn kirɔ mɔ̀ dɑɑ kɔ̃si yi tɔmbɑ koo rɑ ko sɑnɑm dɑ̃ɑkim sɔɔn sɔ̃. 
\is1 Tire ten kpunɑɑ 
\iq1 1. Tɔbiribu, wiru 1:1-2. 
\iq1 2. Pɔlu u Timɔte kirɔ mɔ̀ u n kɑ sɑ̃ɑ nɑɑnɛɡii, wiru 1:3n di sere wiru 2:26. 
\iq1 3. Tɔmbɑ koo Gusunɔn ɡɑri siki, wiru 3:1-9. 
\iq1 4. Pɔlun wɑ̃ɑru, wiru 3:10n di sere wiru 4:8. 
\iq1 5. Gɑri dɑ̃ɑki, wiru 4:9-22. 
\ie  
\c 1  
\s1 Tɔbiribu 
\p  
\v 1-2 Nɑ nun tire teni kuɑmmɛ Timɔte, nɛn bii kĩnɑsi. Gusunɔ Bɑɑbɑ kɑ Yesu Kirisi bɛsɛn Yinni bu nun durom kɑ wɔnwɔndu kuɑ kpɑ bu nun ɑlɑfiɑ kɛ̃. Nɛnɑ Pɔlu, wi Yesu Kirisi kuɑ win ɡɔro Gusunɔn kĩru sɔɔ, n kɑ wɑ̃ɑ te sɑ mɔ Yesu Kirisin min din nɔɔ mwɛɛru kpɑrɑ. 
\s1 Siɑrɑbu kɑ dɑm kɛ̃ru 
\p  
\v 3 Nɑ Gusunɔ sɑɑbu kuɑ wi nɑ sɑ̃ɑmɔ kɑ lɑɑkɑri tɑɑrɛ sɑriruɡiɑ nɡe mɛ nɛn sikɑdobɑ bɑ rɑɑ kuɑ. Nɑ rɑ n mɑɑ nun yɑɑyɑmɔ nɛn kɑnɑru sɔɔ bururu kɑ yokɑ.  
\v 4 Nɑ wunɛn yĩresu yɑɑye mɑ nɑ kĩ n nun wɑ ɡem ɡem kpɑ nɛn ɡɔ̃ru dobu bu kɑ yibu.  
\v 5 Nɑ wunɛn nɑɑnɛ dokebu yɑɑye bi bu ǹ murɑfitiru mɔ. Bin bweserɑ wunɛn nikurɔ Loisi kɑ wunɛn mɛro Enisi bɑ rɑɑ mɔ. Nɑ yɛ̃ kɑm kɑm mɑ ɑ mɑɑ bu mɔ.  
\v 6 Yenin sɔ̃nɑ nɑ nun yɑɑyɑsiɑmɔ, ɑ kɛ̃ɛ te dɔ̃ɔ yɑbio te Gusunɔ u nun wɛ̃ sɑnɑm mɛ nɑ nun nɔmɑ sɔndi.  
\v 7 Domi hunde ye Gusunɔ u sun wɛ̃ yɑ ǹ koo de su bɛrum ko, yɑ koo dewɑ sɑ n dɑm kɑ kĩru kɑ ɡɑyɑ mɔ. 
\p  
\v 8 Yen sɔ̃, ɑ ku bɛsɛn Yinnin seedɑ dibun sekuru ko, ɑ ku mɑɑ nɛn tiin sekuru ko nɛ wi nɑ wɑ̃ɑ pirisɔm dirɔ win sɔ̃. Adɑmɑ ɑ de sɑ n bɔnu mɔ sɑnnu nɔni swɑ̃ɑru sɔɔ Lɑbɑɑri ɡeɑn sɔ̃ nɡe mɛ Gusunɔ u nun yen dɑm wɛ̃ɛmɔ.  
\v 9 Wiyɑ u sun fɑɑbɑ kuɑ mɑ u sun sokɑ sɑ n kɑ sɑ̃ɑ win tiin tɔmbu, n ǹ mɔ ye bɛsɛn tii sɑ kuɑn sɔ̃ mɑ n kun mɔ win himbɑ kɑ win durom sɔ̃ mɛ u sun kuɑ Yesu Kirisin min di sɑɑ toren di.  
\v 10 Tɛ̃, bɛsɛn Fɑɑbɑ kowo Yesu Kirisin nɑɑrɑ sun durom mɛ sɔ̃ɔsi. Domi u ɡɔɔn dɑm kpeesiɑ mɑ u wɑ̃ɑru te tɑ ku rɑ kɑm ko sɔ̃ɔsi Lɑbɑɑri ɡeɑn min di. 
\p  
\v 11 Gusunɔ u mɑn kuɑ ɡɔro kɑ keu sɔ̃ɔsio n kɑ Lɑbɑɑri ɡeɑ ye kpɑrɑ.  
\v 12 Yen sɑɑbun sɔ̃nɑ nɑ nɔni swɑ̃ɑ teni wɑɑmɔ. Adɑmɑ sekurɑ kun mɑn mɔ̀, domi nɑ yɛ̃ wi nɑ nɑɑnɛ doke, nɑ mɑɑ yɛ̃ kɑm kɑm u koo kpĩ u ye u mɑn kereɑ kɔ̃su sere tɔ̃ɔ te, tu kɑ turi.  
\v 13 A nɛn sɔ̃ɔsiru nɛnuɔ kɑ nɑɑnɛ dokebu Yesu Kirisi sɔɔ kɑ kĩi te ɑ mɔ win min di. Sɔ̃ɔsi te, tɑ sɑ̃ɑ ɡɑri ɡee yi nɑ nun nɔɔsiɑ.  
\v 14 Gɑ̃ɑ ɡee ni bɑ nun nɔmɑ bɛriɑ ɑ nu nɛnuɔ kɑ Hunde Dɛɛron dɑm wi u wɑ̃ɑ bɛsɛ sɔɔ. 
\p  
\v 15 Wunɛn tii ɑ nuɑ kɔ mɑ be bɑ wɑ̃ɑ Asin tem sɔɔ, be kpurowɑ bɑ mɑn deri bè sɔɔ Fiɡɛli kɑ Hɛɛmɔɡɛni bɑ wɑ̃ɑ.  
\v 16 Kpɑ Yinni u Onɛsifun yɛnuɡibu wɔnwɔndu kuɑ domi u mɑn dɑm kɑ̃ nɔn dɑbinu. U ǹ mɑɑ nɛn pirisɔm sekuru kue.  
\v 17 Ye u mɑm tunumɑ Romuɔ u mɑn kɑsuwɑ kɑ nuku tiɑ mɑ u mɑn wɑ.  
\v 18 Kpɑ Yinni u de Gusunɔ u nùn wɔnwɔndu kuɑ tɔ̃ɔ te sɔɔ. Wunɛn tii ɑ yɛ̃ sɑ̃ɑ sɑ̃ɑ sɔmɑ ye u kuɑ nɛn sɔ̃ Efesuɔ. 
\c 2  
\s1 Yesu Kirisin tɑbu kowo ɡeo 
\p  
\v 1 Wunɛ mɑɑ nɛn bii, ɑ n tɑ̃sɑ durom mɛ sɔɔ, mɛ sɑ mɔ Yesu Kirisin min di.  
\v 2 Gɑ̃ɑ ni ɑ nuɑ nɛn min di seedɑɡii dɑbinun wuswɑɑɔ, ɑ nu ɡɑbu nɔmu bɛrio be ɑ nɑɑnɛ sɑ̃ɑ be bɑ koo mɑɑ kpĩ bu nu ɡɑbu sɔ̃ɔsi. 
\p  
\v 3 A wuro ɑ ko nɡe Yesu Kirisin tɑbu kowo ɡeo nɔni swɑ̃ɑru sɔɔ.  
\v 4 Tɑbu kowo wi u wɑ̃ɑ tɑbu ɡberɔ, u ku rɑ mɑɑ win wɑ̃ɑrun wunɑnɔ ko yèn sɔ̃ u kĩ u win tɑbu sunɔn kĩru ko.  
\v 5 Wɑsi kɑsɑnuɡii ù n dukɑn ɡɑrɑsɑ mɔ̀, u ǹ kpɛ̃ u yen ɑre wɑ mɑ n kun mɔ u yen woodɑ swĩi.  
\v 6 Mɛyɑ mɑɑ ɡbee wuko wi u sɔmburu kuɑ kɑ wɑhɑlɑ, wiyɑ u ɡinɑ weenɛ u ɡberun mɑrum sɔri.  
\v 7 A nɛn ɡɑri yi kpuro bwisikuo yi nɑ nun sɔ̃ɔmɔ mi, domi Yinni u koo nun somi ɑ kɑ kpuro tubu. 
\p  
\v 8 A Yesu Kirisi yɑɑyo wi u yɑri Dɑfidin bweserun di, mɑ u sikurɑ ɡɔrin di. Win ɡɑri yi wɑ̃ɑ Lɑbɑɑri ɡeɑ sɔɔ ye nɑ wɑɑsu mɔ̀.  
\v 9 Lɑbɑɑri ɡeɑ yen sɔ̃nɑ nɑ nɔni swɑ̃ɑru wɑɑmɔ sere bɑ kɑ mɑn yɔni sɔri nɡe tɔn kɔ̃so. Adɑmɑ bɑ ǹ Gusunɔn ɡɑri sɔri.  
\v 10 Yenin sɔ̃nɑ nɑ kpuro kpĩɑ be bɑ ɡɔsɑn ɑrufɑɑnin sɔ̃, kpɑ ben tii bu mɑɑ fɑɑbɑ wɑ Yesu Kirisin mi kɑ yiiko ye yɑ ku rɑ kpe.  
\v 11 Gɑri nɑɑnɛɡii wee. 
\q1 Sɑ̀ n ɡu kɑ wi sɑnnu, sɑ ko n mɑɑ wɑ̃ɑ kɑ wi. 
\q1  
\v 12 Sɑ̀ n tɛmɑnɑ kɑ suuru, sɑ ko bɑndu di kɑ wi sɑnnu. 
\q1 Sɑ̀ n mɑɑ nùn yinɑ, win tii u koo sun yinɑ. 
\q1  
\v 13 Sɑ̀ n sɑ̃ɑ nɑɑnɛ sɑriruɡibu, kɑ mɛ, u sɑ̃ɑ nɑɑnɛɡii. 
\q1 Domi u ǹ kpɛ̃ u win tii yinɑ. 
\s1 Sɔm kowo wi u tii sɔ̃ɔsi ɡemɡii 
\p  
\v 14 Yeni kpurowɑ kɑɑ wunɛn tɔmbu yɑɑyɑsiɑ kpɑ ɑ mɑɑ bu kirɔ ko Gusunɔn wuswɑɑɔ bu ku sikirinɑ ɡɑri wɛ̃ɛrinun sɔ̃. Domi yenin bweserɑ kun ɑrufɑɑni ɡɑɑ mɔ mɑ n kun mɔ yu tɔmbu kɑm koosiɑ be bɑ swɑɑ dɑki.  
\v 15 A hɑniɑ koowo ɑ n mɔ̀ ye kɑɑ kɑ siɑrɑbu wɑ Gusunɔn wuswɑɑɔ, nɡe sɔm kowo wi sekurɑ kun mɔ̀ win sɔmburu sɔɔ, wi u rɑ n ɡem ɡɑri sɔ̃ɔsimɔ dee dee.  
\v 16 Adɑmɑ ɑ hɑnduniɑn ɡɑri kɑnkɑmɡii suurio, domi yi rɑ tɔmbu dɛsirɑsiewɑ n tomɑ Gusunɔn bɛɛrɛ yɛ̃run di.  
\v 17 Ye tɔn ben bweserɑ sɔ̃ɔsimɔ, yɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ nɡe boo kɔ̃so wi u wɑsi kɔ̃sisiɑmɔ. Be sɔɔrɑ Himɛnɛ kɑ Filɛtu bɑ wɑ̃ɑ.  
\v 18 Bɑ ɡem swɑɑ deri mɑ bɑ ɡɑbun nɑɑnɛ dokebu surɑmɔ, domi bɑ nɛɛ, ɡɔribun seebu sɑrɑ kɔ.  
\v 19 Adɑmɑ kpɛɛkpɛɛku dɑmɡuu ɡe Gusunɔ u surɑ ɡɑ ǹ yĩirurɔ. Gɑri wee yi bɑ yoruɑ ɡen wɔllɔ. Yinni u wiɡibu yɛ̃. Yen biru mɑɑ, bɑɑwure wi u Yinnin yĩsiru soku, u kom kɔ̃sum kpuro derio. 
\p  
\v 20 Dii burɑru sɔɔ ɡbɛ̃ɛ bwese bwesekɑwɑ rɑ n wɑ̃ɑ. Bɑ nin ɡɑnu kuɑ kɑ sii ɡeesu kɑ wurɑ ni bɑ rɑ dendi bu kɑ ɡɑ̃ɑ bɛɛrɛɡinu ko. Bɑ mɑɑ nin ɡɑnu kuɑ kɑ dɑ̃ɑ kɑɑru kɑ sɔndu ni bɑ rɑ dendi bu kɑ ko ye bɑ turɑ.  
\v 21 Bɑɑwure wi u tii sɑ̃rɑsiɑmɔ kom kɔ̃sum di, bɑ koo nùn dendi bu kɑ ɡɑ̃ɑ bɛɛrɛɡinu ko. Domi u sɑ̃ɑ wi bɑ wunɑ nɛnɛm wi Yinni u koo kɑ dendi, u mɑɑ sɔɔru sɑ̃ɑ u kɑ sɔm ɡeeru bɑɑtere ko.  
\v 22 A ɑluwɑɑsirun kĩru kɑnkɑm suurio kpɑ ɑ ɡem kɑ nɑɑnɛ dokebu kɑ kĩru kɑ ɑlɑfiɑ nɑɑ ɡirɑ, wunɛ kɑ be sɑnnu be bɑ Yinnin yĩsiru sokumɔ kɑ ɡɔ̃ru dɛɛrɔ.  
\v 23 Adɑmɑ ɑ tii ɡɑwo sɑɑ wiirɑ ɡɑri kɑ sikirinɔ yɛ̃ru sɑriruɡisun di. A yɛ̃ kɑm kɑm mɑ siyɑ su rɑ sɑnnɔ mɑ.  
\v 24 Wee n ǹ weenɛ Yinnin sɔm kowo u n sɑ̃ɑ nɔɔ ɡɔmunuɡii, ɑdɑmɑ u tɔmbu kpuro dɑɑ ɡeɑ kuo, u n sɑ̃ɑ wi u koo keu sɔ̃ɔsibu kpĩ kpɑ u n dɑ tɛmɑnɛ.  
\v 25 N weenɛ u be bɑ kun kɑ nùn nɔɔ tiɑ sɑ̃ɑ ɡerusi tɛɛru. Sɔrɔkudo Gusunɔ u koo de bu ben ɡɔ̃ru ɡɔsiɑ kpɑ bu ɡem ɡiɑ.  
\v 26 Sɑnɑm mɛyɑ ben lɑɑkɑri koo wurɑmɑ kpɑ bu kisirɑ Setɑm yinɑn di wi u rɑɑ bu nɛni u toorimɔ win ɡɔ̃ru kĩru sɔɔ. 
\c 3  
\s1 Sɑnɑm dɑ̃ɑkim 
\p  
\v 1 A n yɛ̃ mɑ sɑnɑm dɑ̃ɑkim sɔɔ wɑ̃ɑrɑ koo sɛ̃siɑ.  
\v 2 Tɔmbu bɑ ko n ben tii tɔnɑn ɑrufɑɑni kɑsu, ɡobin kĩrɑ ko n bu nɛni, bɑ ko n sɑ̃ɑ woo kɑnɔbu kɑ tii suobu kpɑ bɑ n Gusunɔ ɡɑri kɑm ɡerusimɔ. Bibu bɑ ǹ koo ben mɔwɔbu mɛm nɔɔwɑ, tɔmbɑ ko n sɑ̃ɑ ɡuturubɑ kɑ Gusunɔn bɛɛrɛ yɛ̃ru sɑriruɡibu.  
\v 3 Bɑ ko n sɑ̃ɑ kĩru kɑ wɑnum sɑriruɡibu. Bɑ koo tɔmbu mɛm mɑni kpɑ bɑ n sɑ̃ɑ mɔru kɑnkɑmɡibu be bɑ nɔni tɑu. Bɑ ko bɑ n ɡeɑn kowobu tusɑ.  
\v 4 Bɑ ko n sɑ̃ɑ kɔrumɔtɔnuɡibu kɑ lɑsɑbu sɑriruɡibu kɑ be bɑ tii sue bɑ ɡɑ̃ɑmɔ. Bɑ ko n hɑnduniɑn dobun kĩru mɔ n kere Gusunɔn kĩru.  
\v 5 Bɑ ko n sɑ̃ɑ bèn Gusunɔ sɑ̃ɑrɑ sɑkuɑ, bɑ ǹ koo ten dɑm wurɑ. A tɔn ben bweseru suurio.  
\v 6 Ben ɡɑbɑ ko n yɛnusu duurimɔ kpɑ bu kɑ ben ɡɑri tɔn kurɔ dɑm sɑriruɡibu kɑmiɑ, bèn durum yɑ derɑ bɑ kom yɑɑ bie mɑ bɑ kĩru bɑɑtere diiriɑmmɛ.  
\v 7 Bɑɑdommɑ kurɔ be, bɑ kɑsu bu ɡɑ̃ɑnu ɡiɑ ɑdɑmɑ bɑ ǹ kpɛ̃ bu ɡem ɡiɑ.  
\v 8 Nɡe mɛ Yɑnɛsi kɑ Yɑmbɛsi bɑ kɑ Mɔwisi kinɛnu kuɑ, nɡe mɛyɑ tɔn be, bɑ mɑɑ kɑ ɡem kinɛnu mɔ̀, bɑ ǹ mɑɑ biti mɔ kɔ̃sɑn bwisikunun sɔ̃. Bɑ ǹ ɡɑru koorɔ nɑɑnɛ dokebu sɔɔ.  
\v 9 Adɑmɑ ben hɑniɑ kun kɑ bu ɡɑm dɔɔ, domi bɑɑwure u koo ben wiirɑru wɑ nɡe mɛ n Yɑnɛsi kɑ Yɑmbɛsi deemɑ. 
\s1 Yiire dɑ̃ɑkibu 
\p  
\v 10 Adɑmɑ wunɛ Timɔte, ɑ nɛn sɔ̃ɔsiru kɑ nɛn kookoosu wɑ, kɑ nɛn himbɑ hɑnduniɑn wɑ̃ɑru sɔɔ kɑ nɛn nɑɑnɛ dokebu kɑ nɛn suuru kɑ nɛn kĩru kɑ mɑɑ nɛn tɛmɑnɑbu,  
\v 11 kɑ bɔnɛ ye bɑ mɑn dɔre kɑ nɛn nɔni swɑ̃ɑ te tɑ mɑn deemɑ Antiɔsiɔ kɑ Ikonimuɔ kɑ Lisitiɔ. Bɔnɛ ɡɑɑ sɑri ye nɑ kun wɑ mi. Adɑmɑ Yinni u mɑn yɑkiɑ sɑɑ ye kpuron di.  
\v 12 Kɑ ɡem, bɑɑwure wi u kĩ u Gusunɔ bɛɛrɛ wɛ̃ wi kɑ Yesu Kirisin wɑ̃ɑsinɑɑ sɔɔ, u ǹ koo ko u kun nɔni swɑ̃ɑru wɑ.  
\v 13 Adɑmɑ tɔn kɔ̃sobu kɑ wee kowobu ben kɔ̃suru tɑ ko tɑ n sosimɔwɑ. Nɡe mɛ bɑ ɡɑbu nɔni wɔ̃kumɔ, mɛyɑ bɑ mɑɑ tii nɔni wɔ̃kumɔ.  
\v 14 Adɑmɑ wunɛ, ɑ n ɡɑ̃ɑ ni nɛni ni bɑ nun sɔ̃ɔsi ni ɑ nɑɑnɛ doke. A yɑɑyo tɔn bèn min di wunɛn yɛ̃ru tɑ wee.  
\v 15 Sɑɑ wunɛn birun diyɑ ɑ Gusunɔn ɡɑri yɛ̃ yi yi koo kpĩ yi nun bwisi kɛ̃ ɑ kɑ Yesu Kirisi nɑɑnɛ doke kpɑ ɑ fɑɑbɑ wɑ.  
\v 16 Gusunɔn ɡɑri kpuro yi weewɑ sɑɑ Gusunɔn min di. Yi mɑɑ ɑrufɑɑni mɔ yi kɑ ɡem sɔ̃ɔsi, kpɑ yi kɑ tɔnu win torɑnu sɔ̃ɔsi, kpɑ yi kɑ nùn sɛɛyɑsiɑ, kpɑ yi mɑɑ nùn sɔ̃ɔsi nɡe mɛ u ko n kɑ wɑ̃ɑ ɡem sɔɔ.  
\v 17 Kpɑ Gusunɔɡii u kɑ ko tɔn ɡiro wi u sɔɔru sɑ̃ɑ u kɑ sɔm ɡeeru bɑɑtere ko. 
\c 4  
\p  
\v 1 Nɑ nun yiiremɔ kɑ ɡem Gusunɔn wuswɑɑɔ kɑ Kirisi Yesun wuswɑɑɔ wi u koo wɑsobu kɑ ɡɔribu siri, nɑ mɑɑ nun yiiremɔ win wurɑmɑru kɑ win bɑndun sɔ̃,  
\v 2 ɑ Gusunɔn ɡɑri wɑɑsu koowo ɑ n sɔɔru sɑ̃ɑ bɑɑ ǹ n mɛren nɑ, bɑ wurɑ bɑ ǹ wure. A bu kɑbiɑ buo, ɑ bu ɡerusio, kpɑ ɑ bu dɑm kɛ̃ kɑ suuru bɑkɑ, kpɑ ɑ n bu Gusunɔn ɡɑrin keu sɔ̃ɔsimɔ.  
\v 3 Domi sɑɑ ɡɑɑ wee yè sɔɔ tɔmbɑ kun ko n kĩ bu sɔ̃ɔsi ɡeeru swɑɑ dɑki, ɑdɑmɑ bɑ koo ben tii keu koosio dɑbinu kɑsuɑ be bɑ koo ben swɑɑ nukiri kɑ ɡɑri yi bɑ nɔɔbu kĩ,  
\v 4 kpɑ bu ben swɑɑ sĩiyɑ sɑɑ ɡem di bu wurɑ ɡɑri yi tɔmbɑ sekɑ sɔɔ.  
\v 5 Adɑmɑ wunɛ, ɑ de ɑ n yɛ̃ ye ɑ mɔ̀ kpuro sɔɔ. A kɑ nɔni swɑ̃ɑru tɛmɑnɔ, ɑ Lɑbɑɑri ɡeɑn wɑɑsu kowon sɔmburu koowo, ɑ mɑɑ wunɛn sɔmɑ yibio mɑm mɑm. 
\p  
\v 6 Adɑmɑ nɛ mɑɑ, nɛn wɑ̃ɑrɑ kuɑ nɡe domɑ tɑm, nɛn sɑɑ yɑ turuku kuɑ ye kon kɑ duniɑ deri.  
\v 7 Nɑ tɑɑ ɡeebu kuɑ nɑ kpɑ, nɑ mɑɑ turɑ yɔ̃rɑ yerɔ, nɑ nɑɑnɛ dokebu nɛni dim dim.  
\v 8 Tɛ̃, nɑsɑrɑn ɑre mɑn mɑrɑ, yi yi sɑ̃ɑ ɡem mɛ Yinni siri kowo ɡemɡii koo mɑn wɛ̃ tɔ̃ɔ te. N ǹ mɔ nɛ tɔnɑ, kɑ be kpurowɑ be bɑ win wurɑmɑru mɑrɑ kɑ kĩru. 
\s1 Ye Pɔlu u mɑɑ Timɔte yiire 
\p  
\v 9 A kookɑri koowo ɑ mɑn nɑɑmwɛmɑ ɑ ku tɛ.  
\v 10 Domi Demɑsi u mɑn deri u doonɑ Tɛsɑlonikɑ ɡiɑ yèn sɔ̃ u hɑnduniɑn kĩru mɔ too. Kɛrɛsɑnsi u doonɑ wi mɑɑ Gɑlɑti ɡiɑ, mɑ Titun tii mɑɑ dɑ Dɑrumɑsi ɡiɑ.  
\v 11 Luku turowɑ kɑ mɑn wɑ̃ɑ mini. À n sisi ɑ de i nɑ kɑ Mɑɑku sɑnnu, domi u koo kpĩ u mɑn somi nɛn sɔmburu sɔɔ.  
\v 12 Nɑ Tisiki ɡɔrɑ Efesuɔ.  
\v 13 À n wee, ɑ nɛn woorun yɑberu tɑmɑ te nɑ deri Torɑsiɔ Kɑɑpusin wɔɔrɔ, kɑ mɑɑ nɛn tirenu, n ku mɑm ko ni bɑ kuɑ kɑ ɡɔnɑ. 
\p  
\v 14 Alesɑndu seko wi, u mɑn kɔ̃sɑ kuɑ ɡem ɡem. Yinni u koo nùn kɔsie ye u kuɑ.  
\v 15 A tii lɑɑkɑri koowo kɑ wi, domi u kɔ̃ruɑ ɡem ɡem u bɛsɛn ɡɑri yinɑ. 
\p  
\v 16 Goo sɑri wi u kɑ mɑn yɔ̃rɑ nɔn ɡbiikiru ye nɑ kɑ tii yinɑmɔ, be kpurowɑ bɑ mɑn deri. Gusunɔ u ku ye ɡɑrisi ben wirɔ.  
\v 17 Adɑmɑ, Yinni kɑ mɑn yɔ̃rɑ u mɑn dɑm kɑ̃ nɑ kɑ kpĩɑ nɑ Lɑbɑɑri ɡeɑ wɑɑsu kuɑ tɔn tukobu kpuron wuswɑɑɔ. Nɑ mɑɑ yɑrɑ ɡbee sunɔn nɔɔn di.  
\v 18 Yinni koo mɑn yɑkiɑ sɑɑ kɔ̃sɑ kpuron di kpɑ u kɑ mɑn du win bɑndu sɔɔ wɔllɔ kɑ ɑlɑfiɑ. Wiyɑ yiiko mɔ sere kɑ bɑɑdommɑɔ. Ami. 
\s1 Nɔɔ kɑnɑbu 
\p  
\v 19 Nɑ Pirisilɑ kɑ Akilɑsi tɔburɑ kɑ mɑɑ Onɛsifun yɛnuɡibu.  
\v 20 Erɑsutu u yɔ̃rɑ Korintiɔ, nɑ mɑɑ Torofimu deri Miletuɔ yèn sɔ̃ u bɑrɔ.  
\v 21 A kookɑri koowo ɑ nɑ woorun sɑɑ yu sere turi. 
\p Ebulusi kɑ Pudɛnsi kɑ Linusi kɑ Kolodiɑ kɑ bɛsɛɡibu kpuro ɡesi bɑ nun tɔburɑ. 
\p  
\v 22 Yinni u n kɑ nun wɑ̃ɑ. 
\p Kpɑ Gusunɔn durom mu n kɑ bɛɛ kpuro wɑ̃ɑ.